        "summary": "## Goal\n- Fix issues in the AHV QLHV projects (`ahv-qlhv-fe`, `ahv-qlhv-be`) and MAIY Tech Hub ecosystem according to user requests, with branch-per-task and commit-only workflow.\n- Maintain uptime of services: report portal (8790), MAIY Tech Hub frontend (3000), MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000).\n- Implement: (1) end_date >= start_date validation, (2) max_students limit on student assignment, (3) exam batch form error hiding after field fix, (4) overdue course milestone detection.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Always use prompt-optimizer first to clarify, then confirm with user, then implement.\n- Do not type code directly unless via workflow/agent when possible.\n- Must **checkout a new branch before doing work**.\n- Must **not push**. Only **commit** after finishing.\n- Local only agent ecosystem, no GitLab push.\n- MongoDB only, no PostgreSQL.\n- User language preference: Vietnamese.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **DAT action disabled on Progress page without enrollment** — `fix/progress-dat-disable-without-enrollment-20260423` → `aedf1f6`\n- [x] **Health check persistence fix in backend** — `fix/health-profile-update-persist-20260423` → `46afadc`\n- [x] **Add-student course/rank sync** — `fix/student-add-course-rank-sync-20260423` → `963244c`\n- [x] **\"Đợt thu phí\" settings tab was hidden** — `fix/restore-fee-batch-settings-tab-20260423` → `39f0595`\n- [x] **Synced Student Detail DAT form with Progress page DAT form** — `fix/sync-student-detail-dat-form-with-progress-20260423` → `b499906`\n- [x] **Frontend API base URL for external VPS access** — `fix/external-login-api-base-url-20260423` → `5c6dfe3`\n- [x] **Backend CORS whitelist for external frontend** — `fix/allow-external-fe-cors-20260423` → `48d97e5`\n- [x] **DAT forms — duration/timeStart/timeEnd independent + cross-validation** — `fix/dat-duration-independent-validation-20260423` → `782c1bc`\n- [x] **Tuition/fee field optional in student profile forms** — `fix/tuition-fee-optional-20260423-20260423-2` → `504a89c`\n- [x] **Health check form required fields + validation messages** — `fix/health-check-required-fields-20260423` → `2275548`\n- [x] **Excluded teacher accounts from student list (backend)** — `fix/exclude-teachers-from-student-list-20260423` → `3aa9d86`\n- [x] **Hided \"Mã HV\" column from student list** — `fix/hide-student-code-column-20260423` → `6eae2ba`\n- [x] **Course milestone banner on teacher dashboard (NEW FEATURE)** — BE: `feat/course-milestone-notification-20260423` → `49cdcb1`; FE: `feat/course-milestone-banner-20260423` → `20ff74e`\n- [x] **Task 1 — End date >= start date validation** — BE + FE; `AddCourseModal.tsx` validate function + `course.service.ts` createCourse/updateCourse\n- [x] **Task 2 — Max students limit on assignment** — FE `courses/page.tsx` check in `handleAssign` + BE `course.service.ts` `assignStudentsToCourse` validation\n- [x] **Task 3 — Exam batch form error hiding after field fix** — Already worked; fixed `touch()` in `ExamModal.tsx` + `AddGraduationExamModal.tsx` to pass updated form to validation so error clears instantly on stadium selection\n- [x] **Overdue course milestone detection** — BE returns `overdueOpeningCount` + `overdueClosingCount`; FE shows amber \"quá hạn\" badge; `fix/course-date-validation-max-students-20260423` → `99ebb02` (BE), `fix/course-date-validation-20260423` → `7ba810e` (FE)\n- [x] **Critical fix — wrong collection name** — Backend used `courseinfos` but actual collection is `courses`; fixed in `course.service.ts` getTodayMilestones pipeline → BE: `fix/exam-batch-required-validation-20260423` → `332c4f3`\n- [x] **Critical fix — frontend role check** — Banner was reading `localStorage.getItem('user')` which was always null (AuthContext only stores token, not user object); now uses `useAuth()` hook + added `user` to useEffect dependency array → FE: `fix/course-date-validation-20260423` → `da1457f` + `cd4fe65`\n- [x] **Demo banner page** — `/demo-banner` standalone page for preview; `fix/course-date-validation-20260423` → `ee2d495`\n- [x] **Teacher password reset** — `teacher@qlhv.vn` password reset to `teacher123` via MongoDB bcrypt hash update\n- [x] **EMFILE fix** — Killed hundreds of MAIY BE ts-node processes consuming all file watchers\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **Confirm overdue draft course visibility** — User said they don't see overdue draft courses; HEE draft course (start: 2026-04-22) exists but is assigned to `lihn123`, not `teacher@qlhv.vn`. System is working correctly (only shows teacher's own courses). User asked about `lihn123` account.\n\n### Blocked\n- MAIY Tech Hub backend (4000) crashes on startup: `FastifyError: Plugin did not start in time: 'mongodb'`. Monitor will restart but will keep failing until root cause is fixed.\n- FE production build blocked by existing repo issue: `Cannot find module '@playwright/test'` in `playwright.config.ts`.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Health check data belongs to enrollment**: Root cause was backend enrollment-linked persistence logic.\n- **Student Detail DAT blocked at UI when no enrollment**: Prevent invalid add flow instead of relying on backend failure.\n- **Duration and time fields are independent with submission-time validation**: User explicitly wants no auto-sync between duration and time fields; only validate `duration <= (end - start)` on submit.\n- **Tuition/fee always optional**: Filtered both `'tuition'` and `'fee'` from `requiredConfig` — even if settings marks it as required, it should never be enforced.\n- **Course milestone notification is a dashboard banner, not a popup**: Non-blocking card on dashboard.\n- **Overdue courses included in milestone detection**: `start_date < today && status = draft` = overdue opening; `end_date < today && status = ongoing` = overdue closing.\n- **Banner reads role from `useAuth()` not localStorage**: AuthContext stores user in React state only, not localStorage. Using localStorage always returned null.\n- **Teacher-specific milestones**: API filters by `teacher_id` in `coursestudents` — teachers only see their own courses.\n- **`touch()` must pass updated form to validate**: React state batching means `validate({ ...form })` in closure captures stale form state. Pass `updatedForm ?? form` to fix.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Resolve overdue draft course visibility — user needs `lihn123` account password, or create a test draft course assigned to `teacher@qlhv.vn`\n2. Squash/gang related fix branches before user pushes\n3. Fix MAIY Tech Hub backend MongoDB plugin startup timeout (port 4000)\n4. Remove `demoMode` prop from `Dashboard.tsx` after user approves the banner design\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Accounts**:\n  - `teacher@qlhv.vn` / `teacher123` (password reset) — teacher role, 1148 enrollments, no overdue draft courses assigned\n  - `lihn123` — has HEE draft course (start: 2026-04-22, overdue), password unknown\n  - `admin@qlhv.vn` / `admin123` — superadmin role\n- **Database state (2026-04-23)**: 13 courses were updated from `ongoing → completed` (overdue closing); 2 courses still `ongoing`; 4 courses `draft`; overdue draft course HEE assigned to `lihn123`\n- **BE `.env**: `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=dtlx`, `JWT_SECRET=super_secret_jwt_key_at_least_32_chars_1234`, credentials: `root` / `RYLoQJqsDr4EQIJB`\n- All new AHV QLHV commits are **unpushed** — user has not pushed any of today's changes\n- Course `status`: `'draft'` = \"Sắp khai giảng\", `'ongoing'` = \"Đang học\", `'completed'` = \"Đã kết thúc\"\n- Teacher accounts excluded from student list via `$match: { '_user.role': { $ne: 'teacher' } }` in aggregate pipeline\n- `demoMode` prop on `CourseMilestoneBanner` was disabled in `Dashboard.tsx` — banner now shows real data\n- **Live BE**: PID 720057 (restarted at 18:10), **Live FE**: PID 720730 (restarted at 18:17)\n- Demo page at `/demo-banner` still accessible for design preview\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser reported that `teacher@qlhv.vn` has a course with code A11 that has passed its start date but is still in \"Sắp KG\" (draft) status — not updated to \"đang học\" (ongoing) — and should appear in the overdue milestone banner.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Found course A11 (\"khóa test22/4\") in MongoDB: `status: draft`, `start_date: 2026-04-23`, `teacher_id: null` (not assigned to anyone).\n- Root cause #1: The milestone API only queried `coursestudents` records with `teacher_id = teacherOid`, missing records with `teacher_id: null`. Fixed by changing the match to `{ $or: [{ teacher_id: teacherOid }, { teacher_id: null }] }`.\n- Root cause #2: The overdue query used `{ $lt: today }` but `start_date` equals today exactly (midnight UTC), so the `<` comparison excluded it. Fixed to `{ $lte: today }` for both `start_date` (overdue opening) and `end_date` (overdue closing).\n- After fixes, API returned A11 in the milestone — but it appeared in **both** \"khai giảng hôm nay\" and \"quá hạn\" categories (duplicate).\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe retained suffix shows the next fix: adding deduplication by `course._id` to prevent the same course from appearing in both \"today\" and \"overdue\" arrays. The code adds `seenOpening`/`seenClosing` Sets to filter duplicates before returning, and updates `openingCount`/`closingCount` to reflect unique course counts.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/application/services/dat.service.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/course_student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/dat_session.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/mongodb.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/repositories/course.repository.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2