        "summary": "## Goal\n1. Fix and maintain the OpenClaw team onboarding setup tool (`ahv-openclaw-setup/`) — credentials, skills, agent files, pipe mode\n2. Push a complete, working setup package to a new GitHub branch (`feat/complete-setup`)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly — reply HEARTBEAT_OK if no material changes\n- Use exact workspace path `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md` for heartbeat context\n\n## Progress\n\n### Done\n- [x] Fixed `bin/ahv-setup.js` — `applyCredentials` now sets all 3 Confluence fields: `CONF_BASE_URL`, `CONF_USERNAME`, `CONF_TOKEN` (was only `CONF_TOKEN`)\n- [x] Fixed `bin/ahv-setup.js` — skills unpack: manifest entries are `{agent}/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`; strip leading `{agent}/` prefix and write directly under `destDir` (NOT `destDir/skills/`) to avoid double/triple nesting\n- [x] Fixed `bin/ahv-setup.js` — agent file copy: added `agent-defs/` from setup repo as primary search path (first priority over local workspace paths)\n- [x] Fixed `install.sh` — detect non-TTY (pipe mode) and auto-add `--yes`; updated usage docs\n- [x] Fixed `bin/ahv-setup.js` — team selection: default to `dev` when `skipIntro=true` (pipe mode)\n- [x] Restored `skills.pack` — original committed version (`efb7680`: key=`ahv-openclaw-2026`, 36 entries) was correct; intermediate commit `7d79e2c` had broken pack (key=`None`, 35 entries); local file matched original\n- [x] Fixed `configs/team-*.json` — corrected env var names from old `CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL/CONFLUENCE_API_TOKEN/CONFLUENCE_EMAIL` → correct `CONF_BASE_URL/CONF_TOKEN/CONF_USERNAME`\n- [x] Pushed branch `feat/complete-setup` to `origin` (`git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`)\n- [x] All scripts verified: `node --check` ✅, `bash -n install.sh` ✅, skills decrypt ✅\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Lead needs to create Pull Request on GitHub to merge `feat/complete-setup` → `main`\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **`skills.pack` key mismatch**: Committed version (`7d79e2c`) had key=`None`, 35 entries. Local disk had original correct version (`efb7680`: key=`ahv-openclaw-2026`, 36 entries). Restored from `efb7680`.\n- **Config schema mismatch**: The setup repo (`ahv-openclaw-setup/configs/`) uses old OpenClaw schema with `mcp.servers` (nested), NOT `mcpServers` (top-level). The `applyCredentials` script handles both via fallback: `config.mcpServers || config.mcp?.servers`.\n- **Skills unpack path**: Manifest entries already contain `skills/` directory (e.g., `senior-backend/skills/senior-backend/SKILL.md`). Writing to `path.join(destDir, relativePath)` (without prepending `skills/`) produces correct `~/.openclaw/skills/{agent}/SKILL.md`.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Lead creates GitHub PR: `feat/complete-setup` → `main` at https://github.com/maiychrus25/setup-openclaw/pull/new/feat/complete-setup\n2. Merge PR to `main`\n3. After merge, user setup via `curl | bash` will work correctly with all fixes applied\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Setup repo**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/` — standalone git repo (cloned from `git@github.com:maiychrus25/setup-openclaw.git`)\n- **Current branch**: `feat/complete-setup` (unmerged, pushed to origin)\n- **Last commit**: `2da75cd` — \"fix(setup): all credentials + skills + pipe mode — complete working setup\"\n- **Skills pack**: 36 entries, key `ahv-openclaw-2026`, decrypt formula: `buf[i] ^ key[i % len(key)] ^ (i & 0xff)` → `zlib.inflateSync(dec)`\n- **HEARTBEAT state**: Pipeline HEALTHY, 2 sessions (master-orchestrator:main running, telegram:direct done), no active cron sessions, no blockers. Cron sessions (`cron:ed2d0b5d`, `cron:6f3323ef`) ended normally between 13:33–13:58 UTC.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n## Original Request\nStandard heartbeat poll to check system status and read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Listed active sessions (last 60 minutes): found 5 active sessions\n- Main master-orchestrator session is running (session `267be008`)\n- Another telegram group session is done with several child subagent sessions\n- Tool result was truncated due to size\n\n## Context for Suffix\nHeartbeat health check completed. Multiple sessions are active including the main orchestrator and telegram group sessions with child subagents.\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/install.sh\n</modified-files>",
