        "summary": "## Goal\n1. Maintain and improve the `ahv-openclaw-setup/` onboarding tool — credentials, skills, pipe mode, multi-team support ✅ **COMPLETED**\n2. Build DTLX FE layout redesign: sidebar QLHV-style (glassmorphism, collapsible, tooltips) + new nav labels + logo replacement\n3. Fix login/auth flow for DTLX FE (roles mismatch between backend response and frontend expectations)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly — reply HEARTBEAT_OK if no material changes\n- **`~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` is sacred**: treat as read-only reference; never modify on the running system\n- Use exact workspace path `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md` for heartbeat context\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] **setup-openclaw package COMPLETE**: all 4 team configs generated, `install.sh` final, `skills.pack` (526 entries), pushed to `feat/full-setup-mcp` → force-overridden `main` at commit `12d415d`\n- [x] **Confluence setup guide**: [Hướng Dẫn Lấy API Keys — AHV OpenClaw Setup](https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OTLXPA1/pages/128090113) — covers AHVHOLDING_API_KEY, TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, GITLAB_TOKEN, CONFLUENCE (URL+EMAIL+TOKEN), STITCH_API_KEY\n- [x] Pulled `ahv-dtlx-frontend` from `origin/develop` (`497c986`) into workspace `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend`\n- [x] Created branch `feat/redo-layout` from `origin/develop` for layout redesign work\n- [x] Senior-frontend agent rebuilt sidebar: `SideNav.jsx` rewrite with QLHV-style glassmorphism, `SideNav.css` (new ~400 lines), updated `AdminLayout.jsx` (collapsible state), updated `Header.jsx` (logoPhucAn.png + \"Đào Tạo Lái Xe / DTLX\" badge); all DTLX routes preserved; commit `afa8914`\n- [x] **Login redesign (commit `55f75b7`)**: restored 387-line new Login page (was overwritten to 108-line old version by git stash conflict); verified in working tree via `git cat-file -p HEAD:src/pages/auths/Login.jsx`\n- [x] Installed missing packages: `lucide-react@1.8.0` + `framer-motion@12.38.0` required by new Login design\n- [x] Updated `VITE_API_SERVER=http://103.253.21.139:5555` in `.env` (frontend on Lead's browser → VPS backend)\n- [x] Backend MongoDB `dtlx` was empty (no collections); restarted BE → migration ran → seed data created (roles, users including `admin`)\n- [x] **Fixed 3-role auth bug** (root cause: backend returns `{ doc: { role_name: [\"admin\"] }, ... }` but frontend read `res.roles` → null → 403):\n  - `src/stores/slices/auth.slice.js`: `login.fulfilled` now normalizes: `{ ...payload, ...doc, roles: payload.roles || doc.role_name || [] }`\n  - `setLocalToken`: stores `doc` to `localStorage.user` (not just tokens)\n  - `getLocalUser`: normalizes `role_name` → `roles` for consistency\n  - `loadToken`: sets `authAttempted = true` unconditionally (prevents wipe after login)\n  - `src/pages/auths/Login.jsx`: `const roles = res?.roles || res?.doc?.role_name || []`\n- [x] **DTLX BE credentials**: `admin` / `123456` (from `ADMIN_PASSWORD=123456` in `.env`, `ADMIN_ACCOUNT=admin123@gmail.com`)\n- [x] Dev server running at `http://103.253.21.139:3000/` (Vite on port 3000)\n\n### In Progress\n- [x] Layout redesign committed on `feat/redo-layout` — awaiting Lead review and feedback\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **`feat/redo-layout` branch**: isolated layout work; `origin/develop` (`497c986`) as base; not yet pushed to remote\n- **Auth bug root cause**: backend `signin` response has `role_name` nested inside `doc`, but frontend code expected a top-level `roles` array. Normalized at 3 levels: `auth.slice` (store), `getLocalUser` (localStorage restore), `Login.jsx` (redirect)\n- **MongoDB `dtlx` was empty**: migration runs on BE startup (`CREATE_SAMPLE_DB=true`) and created seed data including the `admin` user\n- **VITE_API_SERVER** must be VPS IP (`103.253.21.139:5555`), not `localhost:5555`, because Lead's browser is on external network\n- **`git stash` conflict**: workspace was converted from `setup-openclaw` repo to `ahv-dtlx-frontend`; `git stash` saved the old working tree which overwrote `Login.jsx` to 108-line old version when `git stash pop` ran — restored via `git cat-file -p HEAD`\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Lead reviews layout** at `http://103.253.21.139:3000/` — collect feedback on sidebar, header, login UI\n2. **Adjust nav labels/structure** if Lead wants changes before committing to feature branch\n3. **Push `feat/redo-layout` to origin** after Lead approval\n4. **Create MR** to merge `feat/redo-layout` into `origin/develop`\n\n## Critical Context\n- **DTLX FE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend`\n- **DTLX BE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend` (running on port 5555)\n- **QLHV FE reference**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe` (Next.js App Router, bootstrap backup — not the live QLHV BE)\n- **Branch state**: `feat/redo-layout` (local only, not pushed); `origin/develop` = `497c986`; commits `55f75b7`/`095a167`/`57f257e` are already in local `feat/redo-layout` history\n- **Backend `.env` (DTLX)**: `PORT=5555`, `MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017`, `MONGODB_NAME=dtlx`, `CREATE_SAMPLE_DB=true`, `ADMIN_PASSWORD=123456`\n- **Frontend `.env` (DTLX)**: `VITE_API_SERVER=http://103.253.21.139:5555`, `VITE_PORT=3000`, `VITE_ALLOWED_HOSTS=localhost,127.0.0.1`\n- **Pipeline**: HEALTHY. Night silence UTC+7 23:00–07:00. Last active: 15:29 UTC.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n## Original Request\nDebugging console errors in a React application (openclaw-tui).\n\n## Early Progress\n- Identified multiple console errors and warnings\n- Found critical uncaught TypeError in `ProtectedRoute.jsx:67` - attempting to call `.includes()` on undefined value\n- Noted Ant Design Dropdown deprecation warning (`overlay` → `menu`)\n- Detected React-Redux selector memoization issue\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe ProtectedRoute component crashes at line 67 when trying to call `.includes()` on an undefined value (likely a permissions/roles array). This causes a cascading failure where the entire ProtectedRoute component fails to render, which prevents the authentication check from completing. As a result:\n- Multiple API calls return 401 Unauthorized errors\n- The user sees \"Vui lòng đăng nhập vào hệ thống!\" (Please login to the system!) error\n\nThe root cause appears to be that user permissions/roles data is undefined when the ProtectedRoute component attempts to validate access.\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/bin/ahv-setup.js\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/install.sh\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/test-pipe.sh\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/config-spec-driven.yaml\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-17.md\n/tmp/patch_install.py\n/tmp/start_dtlx_be.sh\n/tmp/test_setup.sh\n</modified-files>",
