        "tokensBefore": 49811,
        "tokensAfter": 21819,
        "summary": "## Goal\n1. Spawn and initialize fresh sessions for all agents in the AHV DTLX Ecosystem project (agent ecosystem bootstrap)\n2. Read/analyze Figma design for \"CMS Driving Training\" dashboard\n3. Implement new dashboard frontend for `ahv-dtlx-frontend` based on Figma design, pushed to branch `feat/cms-driving-training-design`\n4. Run dev server on port 3002 for user review\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Agent ecosystem is LOCAL ONLY — never push to GitLab\n- Keep MAIY Tech Hub and AHV QLHV Ecosystem sessions intact (only delete DTLX-specific sessions)\n- Frontend repo: GitLab `gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend`, branch `feat/cms-driving-training-design`\n- Tech stack: React + Vite + Ant Design + Redux\n- Image analysis models (TroLy, Opus) are failing with 401/auth errors — Figma design was analyzed via comments + direct screenshot from user\n- Figma MCP rate-limited on file content API; only comments endpoint worked\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Deleted 8 DTLX-specific session transcript files (2 had no files on disk already)\n- [x] Spawned ~36 agents for DTLX ecosystem (gateway kept timing out, many agents got stuck/failed with HTTP 500 or timeout)\n- [x] Confirmed READY agents: senior-frontend, senior-backend, senior-architect (Soren), senior-devops, senior-qa, prompt-optimizer, code-reviewer, security-reviewer (Shield), senior-security (Vigil), playwright-pro, shadcn-expert, content-strategy\n- [x] Analyzed Figma design via comments API — design has: Logo header, sidebar nav, Giáo viên/Học viên stat cards, calendar grid (max 6, scroll/list toggle), chi phí scrollable table, driver info cards\n- [x] Cloned `ahv-dtlx-frontend` repo, created branch `feat/cms-driving-training-design`\n- [x] Installed dependencies (`yarn install` — done in 44.62s)\n- [x] Created `.env` with `VITE_PORT=3002`\n- [x] Dev server running on port 3002 (http://103.253.21.139:3002)\n- [x] Agent spawned to implement dashboard (senior-frontend subagent, session `941483ed-2d30-47aa-9817-f892b2f3fe48` — FAILED with timeout)\n- [x] Agent spawned v2 with detailed code snippets (session `49dcef51-551c-4a1d-af4f-7466d5b4ac38` — status unknown/pending)\n- [x] 4 component files created in `src/pages/dashboard/components/`: `StatsRow.jsx`, `CalendarSection.jsx`, `CostTable.jsx`, `DriverInfo.jsx`\n- [x] Modified `src/index.css` and `src/pages/dashboard/chart/index.jsx`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Waiting for dashboard implementation agent completion (session `49dcef51-551c-4a1d-af4f-7466d5b4ac38`)\n- [ ] Files modified but NOT committed to git yet\n- [ ] Remaining DTLX agents still pending spawn (content-engine, market-intelligence, epic-design, etc.)\n\n### Blocked\n- Figma file content API (rate limited) — couldn't get full file structure, worked around via comments and user-sent screenshot\n- Image analysis models down (TroLy: \"Request aborted\", Opus: 401 invalid x-api-key)\n- Gateway instability caused many agent spawn failures — had to spawn one-by-one\n- senior-frontend agent keeps timing out during implementation (600s timeout not enough)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Figma workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-fe/` created but actual frontend code lives in `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/`\n- **Git monorepo**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/` is the git root; `ahv-dtlx-frontend` is a subdirectory within it (untracked)\n- **Clone needed**: `ahv-dtlx-frontend/` only had `dist` folder — had to `git clone` from GitLab to get source code\n- **Branch**: `feat/cms-driving-training-design` created from `develop` (stash'd old `feat/redo-layout` changes)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for `dtlx:dashboard-impl-v2` agent completion (session `49dcef51-551c-4a1d-af4f-7466d5b4ac38`)\n2. Verify dashboard components compile: `yarn build` in `ahv-dtlx-frontend/`\n3. Check user can see new dashboard at http://103.253.21.139:3002\n4. If agent failed again, implement components manually:\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/StatsRow.jsx` (2 stat cards: Giáo viên, Học viên)\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/CalendarSection.jsx` (grid/list toggle, mock data, max 6 visible)\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/CostTable.jsx` (horizontal scrollable table)\n   - `src/pages/dashboard/components/DriverInfo.jsx` (driver info cards)\n   - Update `src/pages/dashboard/chart/index.jsx` to include new components\n5. Commit changes with `feat(dashboard): implement CMS Driving Training new dashboard design`\n6. Push branch to GitLab for user to create MR\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Frontend repo**: `https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend`, workspace: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/`\n- **Current branch**: `feat/cms-driving-training-design`\n- **Dev server**: running on port 3002 (VITE_PORT=3002)\n- **Dashboard design**: 2 stat cards (Giáo viên/Học viên with 2.000.000₫), Calendar grid (max 6, grid/list toggle), Chi phí table (horizontal scroll), Driver info cards\n- **Figma file key**: `8KT67HAydXovvz3NB5GzgS` — \"Untitled\" by Ngọc Lan Lê Thị + khuong ninh\n- **Figma node IDs**: 26:2326 (calendar), 26:4338 (logo), 26:3059 (scrollable table)\n- **GitLab repos**: `gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend` (frontend), `gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend-morden` (not actively used)\n- **Backend**: `ahv-dtlx-backend/` in same workspace\n- **Stashed changes**: old `feat/redo-layout` branch changes stashed (glassmorphism sidebar work)\n- **MAIY Tech Hub**: separate project at `workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/` (frontend port 3000, backend port 4000) — DO NOT affect\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser Khương Nịnh in group \"AHV DTLX Ecosystem\" reported a CORS error when trying to login. Frontend at `103.253.21.139:3002` cannot access backend at `localhost:5000` due to CORS policy blocking cross-origin requests from public IP to localhost.\n\n## Early Progress\n- **Identified root causes**: Frontend axios defaulted to `localhost:5000` but backend runs on port **5555**; `localhost` unreachable from external browser; **MongoDB not running**\n- **Fixed frontend `.env`**: Changed `VITE_API_SERVER` to `http://103.253.21.139:5555`\n- **Started MongoDB**: Pulled and ran `mongo:4.4` container on port 27017 (MongoDB 7 failed due to CPU AVX incompatibility)\n- **Started backend**: Running `yarn dev` in background session `delta-bloom`\n\n## Context for Suffix\nBackend (`yarn dev` / nodemon) started but last check showed **port 5555 not listening yet**. Need to check if the backend server started successfully, connected to MongoDB, and is now responding, or diagnose any startup errors.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_16---137632a6-7d9a-4ae9-82e7-816c414bd38d.jpg\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/USER.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-18.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-19.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend/.env\n</modified-files>",
